          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1712064263465-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are slightly tender, transfer them to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for an initial 10 min</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1712064268340-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1712064268340-x400.jpg",
